The '''Dudley Award''', named after former [[Virginia Cavaliers football|Virginia Cavalier]] [[Bill Dudley]], is presented annually by the [[Richmond Times-Dispatch]] to one [[NCAA Division I]] [[college football|football]] player in the [[Commonwealth of Virginia]].

